sequenceDiagram
    %% Invoice Registration + Approval + Payment Sequence
    %% Generated by: GitHub Copilot – Claude Sonnet 4.6

    actor ANALYST as Analista Financiero
    actor MANAGER as Gerente Financiero
    actor TREASURER as Tesorero
    participant EXP as accounts-payable-exp-api
    participant INV as invoice-management-api
    participant LFC as invoice-lifecycle-api
    participant ERP as erp-integration-api
    participant PAY as payment-management-api
    participant BANK as banking-integration-api
    participant DB_INV as PostgreSQL:invoices
    participant DB_LFC as PostgreSQL:lifecycle
    participant DB_PAY as PostgreSQL:payments
    participant ERP_SYS as ERP System
    participant BANK_SYS as Banking System

    Note over ANALYST,BANK_SYS: HU-CXP-001: Register Invoice

    ANALYST->>EXP: POST /invoices {supplier_id, invoice_number, amount, ...}
    EXP->>INV: POST /api/v1/invoices
    INV->>ERP: GET /erp/suppliers/{supplierId}/validate
    ERP->>ERP_SYS: GET /suppliers/{id}
    ERP_SYS-->>ERP: 200 {active: true}
    ERP-->>INV: 200 {is_valid: true}
    INV->>DB_INV: INSERT invoice (status=PENDING)
    INV->>LFC: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_state: PENDING}
    LFC->>DB_LFC: INSERT lifecycle + state_transition + audit_log
    LFC-->>INV: 200 {current_state: PENDING}
    INV-->>EXP: 201 InvoiceResponse {status: PENDING}
    EXP-->>ANALYST: 201 InvoiceResponse

    Note over ANALYST,BANK_SYS: HU-CXP-002: Approve Invoice

    MANAGER->>EXP: POST /invoices/{id}/approve
    EXP->>INV: POST /api/v1/invoices/{id}/approve
    INV->>LFC: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_state: APPROVED}
    LFC->>DB_LFC: INSERT state_transition (PENDING→APPROVED) + audit_log
    LFC-->>INV: 200 {current_state: APPROVED}
    INV->>DB_INV: UPDATE invoice SET status=APPROVED
    INV-->>EXP: 200 InvoiceResponse {status: APPROVED}
    EXP-->>MANAGER: 200 InvoiceResponse

    Note over ANALYST,BANK_SYS: HU-CXP-003: Schedule Payment

    TREASURER->>EXP: POST /invoices/{id}/schedule-payment {scheduled_date}
    EXP->>PAY: POST /api/v1/payments {invoice_id, scheduled_date} + X-Idempotency-Key
    PAY->>LFC: GET /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/current-state
    LFC-->>PAY: 200 {current_state: APPROVED}
    PAY->>LFC: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_state: SCHEDULED}
    LFC->>DB_LFC: INSERT state_transition (APPROVED→SCHEDULED) + audit_log
    LFC-->>PAY: 200 {current_state: SCHEDULED}
    PAY->>DB_PAY: INSERT payment_order (status=CREATED)
    PAY->>BANK: POST /banking/payment-orders + X-Idempotency-Key
    BANK->>BANK_SYS: POST /bank-api/payments (mTLS)
    BANK_SYS-->>BANK: 201 {bank_reference}
    BANK->>DB_PAY: Log banking_payment_log
    BANK-->>PAY: 201 BankingPaymentResponse
    PAY->>DB_PAY: UPDATE payment_order SET status=SENT
    PAY-->>EXP: 201 PaymentOrderResponse {status: SENT}
    EXP-->>TREASURER: 201 PaymentOrderResponse

    Note over ANALYST,BANK_SYS: Banking Webhook: Payment Confirmed

    BANK_SYS->>BANK: POST /banking/webhooks/inbound (HMAC-SHA256 signed)
    BANK->>BANK: Validate HMAC-SHA256 signature
    BANK->>BANK: Deduplicate by event_id
    BANK->>DB_PAY: INSERT webhook_event_log
    BANK->>PAY: POST /payments/webhooks/banking {status: CONFIRMED}
    PAY->>LFC: POST /invoice-lifecycle/{id}/transition {to_state: PAID}
    LFC->>DB_LFC: INSERT state_transition (SCHEDULED→PAID) + audit_log
    LFC-->>PAY: 200 {current_state: PAID}
    PAY->>DB_PAY: UPDATE payment_order SET status=CONFIRMED, execution_date=now()
    PAY->>ERP: POST /erp/accounting/entries {invoice_id, amount, payment_date}
    ERP->>ERP_SYS: POST /ledger/entries (OAuth2)
    ERP_SYS-->>ERP: 201 {erp_reference}
    ERP-->>PAY: 201 AccountingEntryResponse
    PAY-->>BANK: 200 OK
    BANK-->>BANK_SYS: 200 OK (webhook acknowledged)
